==English==

===Suffix===
'''-esque'''
# In the [[style]] or [[manner]] of
# [[resembling]]

====Usage note====
This suffix can be added to the end of any noun (common or proper). Eg.
* ''That television show was so weird, almost Monty Pythonesque. ''

